{"tid":1896533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參與功能組別=認同呢個選舉制度背後既邏輯係咩","createTime":"2020-02-25T07:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T08:14:47.000Z","uid":38991,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6af4a3967fbeebfacfeedb162b3260a6cb0f5d3d","tid":1896533,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:41:18.000Z","msg":"呢句野聽左好多年都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係成日比人廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔認同一件事但又參加一件事好似係無矛盾"},{"pid":"999de8fc771dbb9d1a03f021927183bfb54f538a","tid":1896533,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n參加立法會選舉會增加立法會既認受性，外國就無藉口介入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國要揾藉口介入作個理由容乜易<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反我睇唔到杯葛選舉美軍就會即刻出兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60d72f02b66ab62b2bc9ef20cdf0d1489c009820","tid":1896533,"uid":311057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:46:37.000Z","msg":"果班人一係蠢一係就搞分化<br />\n根本點都應該試咗功能組別先，唔試點知唔得？<br />\n好多人話參選可以DQ你<br />\n選到又可以釋法唔俾你做<br />\n咁其實做咩都有風險啦<br />\n街頭抗爭亦有濫捕嘅風險<br />\n香港人就係咩都試先可以成功<br />\n唔好一嚟就自我實現咗先<br />\n你話要廢除功能組別<br />\n呢個都係其中一個方法"},{"pid":"c8f555a16767b5a0680b661e41e2b7e2266c81ff","tid":1896533,"uid":284264,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T07:48:34.000Z","msg":"熱狗邏輯、五毛邏輯"},{"pid":"3db874697a1cf778d5959691811787eedfac7162","tid":1896533,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"求邏輯大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5c2023acc2c7bfc0b4913b01eb4c95429d67d0","tid":1896533,"uid":38991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:09:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cad96849f8c02f496a0a5400478c8f07e442ded","tid":1896533,"uid":179013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"仲有: 參與功能組別=支持認同泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33dcfe00e0067addf74b1cd3d8c61f5bd59efb2c","tid":1896533,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"呢句野第一次聽係08黃教主屌泛民講<br />\n<br />\n利申:,果陣已經聽唔明<br />\n<br />\nps 無謂引戰啦"}]}